title: Captain Insano - The inevitable conclusion to a wasted life
description: Captain Insano are a metal band hailing from Co.Cork in Ireland and formed about 2 years ago from the seeds of various other bands. After a few member changes Captain Insano have never settled on a sound that they are happy with and will continue to experiment and evolve as a unit. In 2005, Captain Insano released their E.P. &#039;&#039;The Inevitable Conclusion To A Wasted Life&#039;&#039;, from which &#039;Doombuggy&#039; is taken. Download it, if you have balls of steel. We&#039;re about to release our new EP, &#039;Howtofakeyourowndeath&#039;, it&#039;s gonna be the tits. It should be out in late April, providing it&#039;s mastered on time. We&#039;ll keep you posted. For more random shit check out www.captaininsanodrinkbuckie.com, you gowls. Cheers, Ken and Captain Insano.
